Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:10.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:21.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:39.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:47.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:54.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:01:00.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:07.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:14.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:21.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:29.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.69,0:01:38.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,They've spotted us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:47.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Retreat at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,The fact that the enemy Simouns\Nshowed up in battle today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:13.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was a taunt to let us know\Nthey can attack us at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:17.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that's exactly\Nwhat they're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:28.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eternal Maidens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:32.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it's really over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,The war, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:40.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,So now we can finally devote our\Nlives to just offering prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:42.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why is it that it doesn't\Nmake us feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to see that other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:24.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one that Grandpa was\Nalways yearning to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,A different world than this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:31.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I became a sibylla,\Nso I could get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:35.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria...\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:41.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then does that mean that Amuria\Nmay also be alive somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:52.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vice Chancellor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:05:01.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please don't call me that.\NThat is no longer my title.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:06.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Though its life may have ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:11.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...this flower can still\Nprovide solace at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Didn't you attend the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:21.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:25.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,The war has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that means it's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:32.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still provide solace, did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I no longer have the power to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:40.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can no longer protect my Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can no longer protect my Neviril.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:47.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are the two conditions set by...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:51.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Shoukoku and the Plumbum highlands\Nin exchange for the ceasefire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever thought to inform me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:57.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're to be treated as their\Nequals, if only on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:06:00.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,And just whose doing would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:03.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Think about it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,"War is foolishness..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:08.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, High Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:19.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,The military governors from\NPlumbum and Shoukoku have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah, we have been waiting for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this really how\Nthings should turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:46.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,All I ever wanted was for the sibyllae\Nto continue praying to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing more...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:51.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,But with this change...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,The way the high priestess\Nwas acting just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:58.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:12.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are they still around when\Nthe peace ceremony is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I heard that some of their forces\Nare staying on the Arcus Prima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:19.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,The more I think of it, the less I\Nunderstand what this "peace" is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:27.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until they found the ancient Simouns,\Nit was their comrades who were dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,So this is what they\Nlook like in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:41.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,All those faces that we\Nextinguished with our Ri Majons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,We never even knew\Nwhat they looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they didn't know what\Nwe looked like either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, the food's\Ngetting cold. Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, Roatreamon, have some of my fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:56.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:08:00.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're getting too thin, you know!\NYou have to get more nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura, you sound like her mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura, you sound like her mom!\NDo I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your legs are in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:13.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get those filthy legs\Nof yours out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:16.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know you can't understand\Na word I'm saying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? I see that you\Nknow I'm insulting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:27.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:45.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:58.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please forgive us,\NSibylla Aurea Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have committed an unspeakable sin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:07.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I bless you. Go in peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:09.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bless us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I bless you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:18.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're in the shower too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:22.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow your soap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:23.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, yours are pretty huge, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:30.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:33.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're always getting in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:37.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Because you're\Ngoing to become a man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to become a man, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to become strong, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can never protect what's dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:51.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know what? Neviril\Ntold me something once...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:59.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,To become strong by being held...\NYou're wrong about that, Alty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:04.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's only when you've\Nboth become strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:07.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that you can truly\Nhold each other close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:17.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I always thought I wanted\Nto become a man too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now I think I can manage\Nwithout making that change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:30.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should accept yourself as you\Nare. Your life will be easier then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia, how did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:17.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know you were at the Ruins,\Nso how in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:22.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you believed that to be true,\Nthen why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:28.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is an extremely\Nunstable place to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins served as the\Ntraining grounds for Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:39.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,So many abortive Emerald Ri Majons\Nexploded into oblivion there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,The helical motors...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:45.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,...are believed to\Nmanipulate time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:47.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,And because of this, Space\Nand Time were distorted...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:55.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,...causing the Spring to exist\Nsimultaneously in two different places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:59.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I find all of this hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:05.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are very few things that\Npeople can actually believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:11.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,...when they are unable\Nto believe in themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:24.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be near my comrades\Nwho had fallen in battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:29.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...yet I was also trying to flee\Nas far away from them as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,But how did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I was the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I shied away from making a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:45.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and tried to run as far\Naway from reality as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:50.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I've been seeking\Nyou out all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:56.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to have someone hear my confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,To hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,...my sins...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:11.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,One of the conditions of our peace\Ntreaty with Plumbum and Shoukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:14.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...calls for the\Ndissolution of Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:38.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where did Yun run off\Nto at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:39.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't want any part of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:43.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest, disbanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all the effort we\Nput into it until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:53.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Plumbum priestesses will be\Ntaking over our duties, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:56.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm confused. Is this what peace is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:59.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can never hope to be on equal terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:02.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:05.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,One thing's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:11.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,They have no use for\Nus anymore. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:21.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just when we finally\Nstarted to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the true meaning of\Nour prayers as sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even after Chor Tempest\Nceases to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:32.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,...nothing can change the fact\Nthat we're all Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:38.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,And nobody will ever debase our prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,If Chor Tempest is disbanded...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:09.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we won't be able to\Nfly the Simouns anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:11.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,The door to that other world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will be closed to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:18.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've always longed to see\Nthat other world, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:27.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't remember you being so talkative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:28.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:37.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:49.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,We haven't talked like\Nthis in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:16:59.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:01.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:06.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you give me your blessing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:07.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:19.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Sulking, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you have a fight with Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why are you\Nasking me about Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right on the money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:47.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,She talks up a storm now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:55.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, you can always use\Nyour mouth to stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:57.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Boy, kissing is all you\Never think about, Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:02.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,You told me it's when you really like\Nsomeone that you want to kiss them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,So don't you want to kiss her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:07.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not the way Neviril is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:10.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't you like her anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ha! You're just jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:19.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on? I feel hot all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, you're in critical condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold up! What do you mean, critical?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,It might not just be Neviril, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,It could be that you've\Nchanged as well, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:54.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:57.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where is Sibylla Aer? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,High Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it, High Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:05.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose you'll do, Sibylla\NParaietta. Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Follow me. Please. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:18.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,High Priestess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:21.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must take off now, Sibylla\NParaietta, Sibylla Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:22.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:26.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no time to lose! You must\Ngo at once! If you don't hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:31.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the door will close on us!\NNever to open again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,The door?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:38.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,A long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I was a member of Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:43.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I dreamed of completing\Nthe Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I dreamed of becoming an eternal maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eternal maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun is much like a maiden herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:58.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,A maiden vacillates...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:03.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun gem reflects\Nthat vacillating soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,A maiden drifts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:10.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Escaping reality for all eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:17.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tracing the skies with\Nher everlasting beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please slow down, Your Eminence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:43.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must change Kyuukoku's fate!\NWe cannot go on like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unless we do something about it, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:46.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry! You must go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,To the Land of Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:56.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:25.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're keeping something\Nfrom me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:32.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:37.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:40.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,As your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:48.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Allow me to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,When one flees from reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:54.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,...refusing to choose a gender...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,...this is what becomes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:48.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:52.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:59.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:07.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:20.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to get closer to you.\NI want to feel your pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.39,0:23:25.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.56,0:23:29.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:33.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:39.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:44.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:48.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:53.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:24:00.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:07.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.40,0:24:11.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril bares her soul to Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.41,0:24:14.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and the other sibyllae make\Ntheir way towards the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:17.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.38,0:24:20.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Choices\NChoices.
